<item>
            <title>[LU-14065] lnet/lnd: dynamically set LND parameters</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14065</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Do an overview of the LND/LNet module parameters and determine which ones we can be set dynamically. There are a category of parameters which can be set dynamically and would be useful to do so to streamline tuning LNet on the fly on active sites:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
peer_credits
peer_credits_hiw
concurrent_sends
service_port
timeout
conns_per_peer
peer_timeout
use_privilaged_port
require_privileged_port
accept_type
avoid_asym_router_failure
alive_router_check_interval
router_ping_timeout&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
